    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "siege_weapon",
        "text": "The arm of this modified catapult ends in three baskets, the aim of which can be adjusted to fling its payload over a wider spread. A shatterpult is usually loaded with specially made \u201cshatterstones,\u201d which are constructed to explode into hundreds of sharp shards upon impact. The jagged pieces of a burst of shatterstones make the ground difficult to cross, similar to a handful of caltrops.",
